4 October 2007Media are informed that Dr Frene Ginwala will later today (Thursday, 4 October 2007), issue a statement regarding the details of the inquiry into the fitness of Advocate Vusumzi Pikoli to hold the office of National Director of Public Prosecutions. Dr Ginwala will not be able to brief the media as was earlier indicated.Dr Ginwala appeals to media to refrain from calling her until the statement is issued.Enquiries Themba Maseko - Government Spokesperson Cell: 083 645 0810Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)